{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_08_02",
  "title": "fran 2話 立派な社会人ですし",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……あー、眠っ。{user}さん\n少しそこのソファ借りますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hohum… ahー‚ sleepy. {user}-san\nI'll borrow that sofa for a while",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかお疲れですね……ここしばらくは\nそこまでスケジュール詰まってなかったと思うんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look so tired… I don't think\nyour schedule was that tight",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事が少なくて悪うございましたね\nそれなら、もっと私の仕事取ってきて下さいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ but I don't have much work to do\nIf you're not satisfied‚ please bring me more work",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりエン』のアニメを、一話から見直してたんですよ\n十年以上続いてるシリーズなので、かなり話数が多くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm binge-watching the \"Pretty★Angel\" the whole series\nIt's a series that's been running for over ten years‚ so there are a lot of episodes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ネクロが出ないとこは飛ばすつもりだったんですけど\n気が付いたら、普通に全部観ちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was planning to skip the parts where Necro doesn't appear‚ but\nbefore I knew it‚ I'd watched the whole thing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……お疲れ様です\nでも大丈夫ですか？　午後から収録ありますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… great job\nBut is it okay? You have a recording this afternoon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "私を誰だと思ってるんです\nこれまで本番でみっともないとこ見せたことあります？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who do you think I am\nHave I ever done anything embarrassing during a live performance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.466666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あとは……そうだ。劇団主催のワークショップに\n参加するので、明後日から行ってきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… yeah. I'm participating in a workshop\nhosted by a theater company‚ so I'll be there the day after tomorrow",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.366666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "私、ステージには飽きるほど立ってきましたけど\nちゃんと演技を勉強したことないですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I stood on stage countless times‚\nbut I've never really studied acting properly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.366666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりエン』の舞台の稽古が始まるまでに\n出来る限りの準備はしておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to prepare as much as I can\nbefore rehearsals for \"Pretty★Angel\" begin",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "だって悪役が格好悪い話なんて、つまらないですしね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because‚ a story where the villain doesn't have any form‚ is not cool!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8295473416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.9467580159
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.9467580159
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.230091351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（その後もfranさんは熱心に演技の勉強に取り組んだ）\n（そしてとうとう、舞台稽古が始まったのだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（fran-san continued to study acting diligently after that）\n（And finally‚ rehearsals began……）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.966666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.966666921
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.6478015582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "今のシーン、もう一度最初からですか？\n一体誰のミスよ……え、私の演技が全然駄目だから！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This scene‚ from the beginning again?\nWhose fault was it…… Eh‚ because my acting was terrible!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことよ、台詞もミスはなかったはずなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a nonsense‚ I also didn't make any mistakes in the lines…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.727797699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.374759388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（演出の蟻田さん、ベテランだし評価も高い人だけど）\n（演技指導が厳しいのでも有名なんだよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The director‚ Arita-san‚ he is a veteran and highly regarded actor）\n（But he was also famous for his strict acting guidance）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9333295187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（franさんもさすがに一発OKとはいかなかったか）\n（大変だけど、ここから少しずつ直していくしか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even Fran-san didn't get it right the first time）\n（It will be difficult‚ but just have to fix it little by little from…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6333295187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5206919989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "納得いきません。理由を説明して下さい\nはぁ……私の台本の読み込みが甘い、ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't understand. Please explain why\nHaa… I'm not good at reading my own script‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7333208722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.4085607212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "このシーンは、今度こそプカミ達に勝てると信じて\n慢心しているシーンなのに、慢心し切れていない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this scene‚ I'm confident that this time I can defeat\nthe Fukami team‚ but you saying I am not confident?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1999875388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "お言葉ですが。原作のアニメでは\n次のシーズンで、新たな四天王候補が出てきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your kind words. In the original anime‚\na new candidate for the Four Heavenly Kings appears in the next season",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.0333208722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.8478971166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "つまり『私』は地位を脅かされている訳です\nですので慢心しているようでいて、内心焦っている……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ \"My\" position is threatened\nSo‚ it seems like I'm confident‚ but on the other hand‚ I'm also anxious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4666257224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ここはそう表現するべきだと判断しました\n他に、何かご質問は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I decided that this is the way to express it\nAny other questions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2332903546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.4205254874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど、franさんなりに考えたプランだった訳か）\n（でも演出家さん相手にあんな偉そうに言わなくても！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see‚ so this was a plan fran-san came up with herself）\n（But you didn't have to act so arrogantly in front of the director!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.0999570212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（初っ端からあんなにやり合って）\n（この舞台、無事に初演までこぎ着けるだろうか……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's been doing whatever she wants from the beginning）\n（Will this stage‚ be able to hold its first play safely…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.5999570212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.7147199316
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.7147199316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "あー、腹立つ。大御所だかなんだか知りませんけど\nあの人、『ぷりエン』のこと全然分かってないんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahー‚ so pissed off. I don't know if he's a big shot or something\nbut that guy doesn't understand \"Pretty★Angel\" at all",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.6332903546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.9247219089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "ネクロは悪役だし考えなしだし人の話聞かないけど\nでも部下には優しいし、いいとこも沢山あるんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Necro is a villain and she's thoughtless‚ and doesn't listen to what others say\nBut she's kind to her servants and has a lot of good points!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.8332923891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
