      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあまあ……しかし、さっきは肝が冷えましたよ\nfranさんがまさか、事務所の外でやり合うとは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ well… by the way‚ that just now scared the crap out of me\nI never thought fran-san would fight outside the office",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.3999631248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
