      "text": "蟻田さんも、一緒に舞台を作る仲間なんですから\nそれにほら、舞台の出演料もなかなかの金額でしたし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Arita-san is also a colleague who's working on the stage together\nAnd look‚ the performance fee was quite a lot!",
